{
  "chapter": "104",
  "title": "田叔列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "出身与入仕",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田叔</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陉城</span>人。他的祖先，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田</span>氏的后裔。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔</span>喜欢<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>术，向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐巨公</span>学习<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">黄老</span>之术。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔</span>为人刻苦廉洁自好，喜欢与诸位贤达交游。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国有人把他举荐给<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵午</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">午</span>又把他推荐给<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张敖</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span>任命他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎中</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数年（时长）</span>，他耿直廉明公正，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span>认为他很贤能，但还没来得及提拔他。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "贯高谋反与从赵王",
      "text": "恰逢<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>地叛乱，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>前往<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>讨，经过<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张敖</span>亲自端着食案进献饮食，礼节十分恭敬，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>却伸开腿坐着傲慢地辱骂他。当时<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵午</span>等<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十人</span>都很愤怒，对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张王</span>说：\"王事奉皇上的礼数已经周全了，现在对待王这样，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>等请求叛乱。\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span>咬破手指出血，说：\"先人失去了国家，如果没有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>等就会成为虫子爬出尸体的人。你们怎么能说这样的话！再也不要说出口了！\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">贯高</span>等人说：\"王是长者，不背弃恩德。\" 最终私下互相谋划<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>杀皇上。事情败露后，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>廷下诏逮捕<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span>和参与谋反的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵午</span>等都<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>，只有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">贯高</span>被捕。当时<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>颁下<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">诏书</span>：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>有敢跟随赵王的，罪及三族。\" 只有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟舒</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田叔</span>等<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀人</span>穿着赭色囚衣，自己剃光头戴上颈枷，假称是赵王的家奴，跟随<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">敖</span>到了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">贯高</span>的谋反案真相大白后，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">敖</span>得以释放，被贬为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">宣平侯</span>，于是向朝廷推荐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田叔</span>等<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀人</span>。皇上全部召见，与他们交谈，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>廷<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>没有能超过他们的，皇上很高兴，全部<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span>他们为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郡守</span>或<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">诸侯相</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔</span>担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉中守</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十多年（时长）</span>，适逢<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高后</span>去世，诸<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕</span>作乱，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>们<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>灭了他们，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文帝</span>。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "荐孟舒为长者",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文帝</span>即位后，召见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田叔</span>问他说：\"您知道<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长者</span>是谁吗？\" 他回答说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>哪里能知道呢！\" 皇上说：\"您是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长者</span>，应当知道。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔</span>叩头说：\"原来的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">云中守</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟舒</span>，是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长者</span>。\" 当时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟舒</span>因为敌虏大举入塞抢劫，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">云中</span>受害尤其严重，被免职。皇上说：\"先帝任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟舒</span>为云中守<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十多年（时长）</span>了，敌虏一入侵，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟舒</span>就不能坚守，使得没有缘故的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>死数百人。长者本来就会让人白白送死吗？您凭什么说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟舒</span>是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长者</span>呢？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔</span>叩头回答说：\"这正是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟舒</span>之所以为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长者</span>的原因。当初<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">贯高</span>等人谋反，皇上明诏颁下，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>有敢跟随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张王</span>的，罪及三族。然而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟舒</span>自己剃发戴枷，跟随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">敖</span>所在之处，想用命为他殉死，难道他自己知道将来会做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">云中守</span>吗！<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>相对峙，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒疲惫不堪。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">匈奴</span>的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冒顿</span>刚刚征服<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">北夷</span>，来侵犯边境为害，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟舒</span>知道<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒疲惫，不忍开口下令，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒争着登城拼死杀敌，像儿子为父亲、弟弟为兄长一样，因此战死的有数百人。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟舒</span>难道是故意驱赶他们去〖◈作战的吗！这正是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟舒</span>之所以为长者的原因。\" 于是皇上说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟舒</span>真贤能啊！\" 又召回<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟舒</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">云中守</span>。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "案梁王杀袁盎事",
      "text": "后来<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔</span>因犯法失去官位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁孝王</span>派人<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了原<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">袁盎</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田叔</span>去审查<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国，全部查清了事情的真相，回来汇报。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>问：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国有这事吗？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔</span>回答说：\"死罪！有的。\" 皇上问：\"事情的证据在哪里？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田叔</span>说：\"皇上不要过问<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国的事了。\" 皇上问：\"为什么？\" 他说：\"现在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁王</span>如果不伏<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>，那就是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>法不能行使；如果让他伏法，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>就会吃不下饭，睡不安席，这忧患就落到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>身上了。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>非常赏识他，任命他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">鲁相</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "为鲁相",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">鲁相</span>刚到任，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众自己来找相，控诉鲁王夺取他们财物的有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百馀人</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田叔</span>抓了他们的为首的<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十人</span>，每人鞭笞<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五十</span>下，其余的各抽打<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十</span>下，愤怒地对他们说：\"鲁王不是你们的主人吗？怎么自己敢说主人的坏话！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲁王</span>听说后非常惭愧，拿出府库的钱，让相去偿还。相说：\"王自己抢夺的，让相来偿还，这是王做了恶事而相做了善事。相不参与偿还。\" 于是鲁王就全部偿还了。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "谏鲁王游猎",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲁王</span>喜欢打猎，相常常跟从进入苑囿，王总是让相到馆舍休息，相出来后，常常顶着烈日坐在苑外等王。王多次派人请相去休息，他始终不休息，说：\"我王在苑中露天暴晒，我为什么独自去馆舍呢！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲁王</span>因此不大出游了。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "卒",
      "text": "过了几年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔</span>在任上去世，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国用<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">百金</span>来祭祀，少子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任安\">仁（任安）</span>不接受，说：\"不能因为<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">百金</span>而损害先人的名誉。\""
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "入仕与升迁",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任安\">仁（任安）</span>凭强壮健硕担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卫将军</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span>，多次跟随<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">匈奴</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卫将军</span>推荐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任安\">仁（任安）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任安\">仁（任安）</span>被任命为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎中</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数年（时长）</span>，升为<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">二千石</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相长史</span>，后失去官位。后来奉使去查核<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三河</span>。皇上东巡，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任安\">仁（任安）</span>奏事时辞辩有力，皇上很高兴，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span>他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">京辅都尉</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一个多月（时长）</span>，皇上又升<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span>他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司直</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数年（时长）</span>，因<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>之事获罪。当时<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左相</span>亲自带兵，命<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司直</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田仁</span>负责守卫<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">城门</span>，因为放走了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，被交付法吏<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀处死。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任安\">仁（任安）</span>也发兵，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长陵</span>令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">车千秋</span>上书告发<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任安\">仁（任安）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任安\">仁（任安）</span>被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">族</span>灭处死。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陉城</span>现在属<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中山</span>国。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>说\"身处一国必能听到其政事\"，说的就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田叔</span>吧！他坚持大义不忘举荐贤者，彰显明主的美德以补救过失。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任安\">仁（任安）</span>与我交好，所以我把他也一并论述。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "任安早年",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">褚先生</span>说：<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>担任郎官时，听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田仁</span>原本和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任安</span>关系很好。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任安</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>人。少年孤苦贫困，替人赶<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>，留了下来，想谋个小吏的职位，没有门路，便冒名挂在户籍上。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武功</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">扶风</span>西边的小县，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">谷口</span>通往<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">刬道</span>靠近山地。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">安</span>认为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武功</span>是个小县，没有豪强，容易出头，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">安</span>便留下来，替人谋求<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">盗亭父</span>的职位。后来做了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">亭长</span>。县中的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众一起出去打猎，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任安</span>常常替人分配<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">麋</span>、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鹿</span>、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">雉</span>、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">兔</span>，分派老小壮弱到难易不等的地方，众人都很高兴，说：\"不用担心，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任少卿</span>分得公平，有智谋。\" 第二天又聚会，聚会的有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数百人</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任少卿</span>说：\"某某人为什么没来？\" 众人都奇怪他察人之快。后来他被任命为<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三老</span>，推举为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">亲民</span>官，出任<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三百石</span>的县令，治理<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众。后来因为皇上出游时所负责的帐幕没有备办好，被斥退免职。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "任安与田仁为舍人",
      "text": "于是他做了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卫将军</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span>，和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田仁</span>一起同任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span>，住在门下，同心相爱。这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人家</span>贫，没有钱送给将军的家监，家监让他们养那些咬人的劣<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>。两人同床而卧，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任安\">仁（任安）</span>私下说：\"家监真是不识人啊！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任安</span>说：\"将军尚且不识人，何况家监呢！\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卫将军</span>带这两人去见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平阳主</span>，公主家的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">家令</span>让两人和骑奴同席吃饭，两位<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>便拔<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">刀</span>把席子割断，另坐一边。公主家里的人都对他们感到奇怪和厌恶，但没人敢呵斥。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "赵禹举田仁任安",
      "text": "后来有诏令募选<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卫将军</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span>为郎官，将军挑了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span>中家境富裕的，让他们备好<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鞍</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">绛衣</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">玉具剑</span>，准备奏呈上去。 恰好贤<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>少府<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵禹</span>来拜访<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卫将军</span>，将军把所举的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span>叫出来让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵禹</span>过目。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵禹</span>依次询问他们，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀人</span>中没有一人熟悉政事又有智谋的。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵禹</span>说：\"我听说，将门之下必有将才。传文说‘不了解国君就看他所使用的人，不了解儿子就看他交的朋友’。如今诏令举荐将军的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span>，是想通过将军得到文武贤者。现在只选富家<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>弟送上去，又无智谋，就像木偶人穿着绮罗绸缎罢了，那怎么办呢？\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵禹</span>把<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卫将军</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百馀人</span>全部召来，依次询问，找到了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田仁</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任安</span>，说：\"只有这两人可用，其他没有可用的。\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卫将军</span>看到这两人贫穷，心里不高兴。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵禹</span>走后，对这两人说：\"你们各自备好<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鞍</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>和<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">新绛衣</span>。\" 两人回答说：\"家里贫穷没有东西可备。\" 将军发怒说：\"现在你们两位自家贫穷，为什么说这样的话？怏怏不乐像对我有什么恩德似的，为什么呢？\" 将军不得已，把他们列入名籍上奏。 有诏令召见<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卫将军</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span>，这两人上前拜见，诏问他们能力大致有什么长处。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田仁</span>回答说：\"手提鼓槌站在军门之前，让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士大夫</span>乐于赴死作战，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任安\">仁（任安）</span>比不上<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任安</span>。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任安</span>回答说：\"决断嫌疑，判断是非，辨别治理官职，让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>没有怨言，我比不上<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任安\">仁（任安）</span>。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>大笑说：\"好。\" 让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任安</span>掌管<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">北军</span>，让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田仁</span>掌管<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>边的屯田。 这两人因此扬名<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "田仁刺举三河",
      "text": "后来任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任安</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">益州刺史</span>，任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田仁</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相长史</span>。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田仁</span>上书说：\"<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郡太守</span>多有营私舞弊的，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三河</span>尤其严重，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>请求先查办<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三河</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三河</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太守</span>都内依宫中<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贵人</span>，和<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三公</span>有亲属关系，无所畏惧，应当先整顿<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三河</span>以警告<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>奸吏。\" 当时<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河南</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">河内太守</span>都是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">杜</span>氏的父兄子弟，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">河东太守</span>是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">石</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>的子孙。当时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">石</span>氏有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">九人</span>做<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">二千石</span>，正是兴盛显贵。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田仁</span>多次上书弹劾。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">杜</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">石</span>氏派人去致歉，对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田少卿</span>说：\"我们不敢多说什么，只愿少卿不要诬陷玷污我们。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任安\">仁（任安）</span>查办完<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三河</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三河</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太守</span>都被下狱<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀处死。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任安\">仁（任安）</span>回来奏报，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>高兴，认为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任安\">仁（任安）</span>能不畏强权，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任安\">仁（任安）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相司直</span>，威名震动<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "田仁纵太子诛死",
      "text": "后来恰逢<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>起兵之事，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>亲自率军，派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司直</span>负责守卫<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">城门</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司直</span>认为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>是骨肉至亲，父子之间不太应该过于逼迫，便离开城门到诸陵一带去了。当时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">甘泉</span>，派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">暴君</span>下来责问<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>\"为什么放走了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>\"，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>回答说：\"让<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司直</span>负责守城门，而他放走了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>\"。上书奏报，请求逮捕<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司直</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司直</span>被下狱，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀处死。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "任安坐观成败诛死",
      "text": "那时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任安</span>担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">北军使者</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">护军</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>在<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">北军</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南门</span>外停<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>，召见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任安</span>，给他节杖让他发兵。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">安</span>拜受节杖后进去，闭门不出。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>听说后，认为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任安</span>耍诈，没有依附太子行事，这是为什么？<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任安</span>曾经笞打侮辱<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">北军钱官</span>的小吏，小吏上书告发他，说他接受了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>的节杖，说过\"希望给我那些鲜好的\"。上书被呈报上去，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>说：\"这是个老吏啊，看见兵事兴起，想<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">坐观成败</span>，见谁胜了就想<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">合从</span>谁，怀有两心。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">安</span>应当死的罪过很多，我常常使他活下来，如今却心怀诈伪，有不忠之心。\" 把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">安</span>下狱，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀处死。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "知进退之论",
      "text": "<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">月满则亏</span>，物盛则衰，这是天地的常理。只知前进而不知后退，长期享受富贵，祸患积聚成为灾祟。所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蠡</span>离开<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>，辞官不受官位，名传后世，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">万年（时长）</span>不被人遗忘，这岂是能赶得上的！后人应当谨慎警戒。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "赞诗",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田叔</span>是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长者</span>，看重大义轻视生命。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张王</span>冤案得到昭雪，出任<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉中</span>太守为荣。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟舒</span>被废，抗辩陈说为他辩明。 审按<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>事以礼相处，做<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>相得民情。 儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任安\">仁（任安）</span>因事获罪，弹劾查办有声名。"
    }
  }
}